  "description": "A Caesar salad typically combines lettuce, croutons, cheese, egg, Worcestershire sauce, anchovies, garlic and black pepper. We've left the anchovies out to make it vegetarian and used capers as a salty, briny replacement, along with green beans and chives. Henderson's relish replaces Worchester sauce because it's vegetarian too!",
